Guided Exercise: Protect External Traffic with TLS
Goal of This Exercise
Main goal:
Expose an application securely using TLS
You will learn:
1.	Deploy application
2.	Create HTTP route
3.	Create TLS Edge Route
4.	Generate TLS certificate
5.	Store certificate in Secret
6.	Mount secret inside Pod
7.	Create Passthrough TLS Route
8.	Verify encrypted communication
________________________________________
