Explanation:
Option	Meaning
expose	create route
svc	service
hostname	public URL
Now architecture:
Internet
   │
Router
   │
Service
   │
Pod
Check route:
oc get routes
Example:
NAME        HOST/PORT
todo-http   todo-http.apps.ocp4.example.com
