7. Capture Network Traffic (HTTP)
Command:
sudo tcpdump -i eth0 -A -n port 80
Explanation:
Option	Meaning
-i eth0	interface
-A	ASCII output
-n	no DNS resolution
port 80	HTTP traffic
When refreshing page you see:
angular.min.js
angular-route.min.js
This proves:
HTTP traffic is visible in plain text
Meaning:
Not secure
________________________________________
8. Create Encrypted Edge Route
Command:
oc create route edge todo-https \
--service todo-http \
--hostname todo-https.apps.ocp4.example.com
Explanation:
Option	Meaning
route edge	TLS edge route
todo-https	route name
service	backend service
hostname	public URL
Architecture:
Client (HTTPS)
      │
      ▼
Router (TLS termination)
      │
      ▼
Service (HTTP)
      │
      ▼
Pod
Encryption:
Client → Router = encrypted
Router → Pod = plain HTTP
