19. Architecture Comparison Learned
HTTP Route
Client → Router → Pod
(no encryption)
________________________________________
Edge Route
Client → Router (TLS)
Router → Pod (HTTP)
________________________________________
Passthrough Route
Client → Router → Pod (TLS)
End-to-end encryption.
